        <h1>About Us</h1>
        
        
        <p>
            Annapurna Premium is an innovative platform that revolutionizes the way surplus food is managed, connecting food providers with consumers and donors to combat hunger and food waste. Building upon the success of our standard Annapurna website, Annapurna Premium offers enhanced features and services tailored to meet the diverse needs of our users.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our mission is simple yet profound: to create a world where no one goes hungry and where surplus food is utilized to its fullest potential. With Annapurna Premium, food providers have the opportunity to sell or donate surplus food on a daily or regular basis, empowering them to generate income while making a positive impact on their communities.
        </p>
        <br>
        
        <p>
            <h1>Key features of Annapurna Premium incluide:</h1>
        </p>
        
        <br>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <b>Subscription-Based Model:</b>
                Annapurna Premium opetrates on a subsctiption-based model,
                allowing food providers to access premium features and services for 
                a nominal monthly fee of approximately one dollar.
                Subscribers gain access to enhanced funcitonalities designed to streamline 
                the process of selling surplus food and reaching a broader audience.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Flexible Listing Options:</b> 
                Food providers have the flexiblity to list surplus food items for sale or 
                donation on Annapurna Premium. New users can list their items for free up to three times,
                after which a subscription is required for continued access to premium services. 
                However, there are no limitations on the number of times users can donate surplus food for free.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Secure Payment Processing:</b>
                Annapurna Premium facilitates secure payment transactions between food providers and consumers,
                ensuring the confindentiality and integrity of financial information.
                Our platform partners with truseted payment processors to offer seamless and realiable payment 
                processing services.

            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Community Engagement:</b>
                Annapurna Premium fosters community engagement by connecting food
                providers, consumers, and donors in a collaborative effort to address hunger and food waste.
                Through our platform, users can participate in meaningful exchanges that benefit both individuals
                and society as a whole.
            </li>
            <li>
                <b>Privacy and Securtiy:</b>
                We proiritize the privacy and security of our user's data, employing industry-standard measures
                to protect against unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.
                Our Privacy Policy outlines hhow we collect, use, and safeguarad personal information in accordate
                with legal and ethical standards.

            </li>
        </ol>
